{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01AotoGN6k85tsonDfQ5VMxV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Looking at this problem, we need to show for every positive integer $n$:\n$$\\left(\\frac{2n-1}{e}\\right)^{(2n-1)/2} < 1 \\cdot 3 \\cdot 5 \\cdots (2n-1) < \\left(\\frac{2n+1}{e}\\right)^{(2n+1)/2}$$\n\n**Setup.** Let $P_n = 1 \\cdot 3 \\cdots (2n-1)$. Define $f(x) = x\\ln x - x$, so $f'(x) = \\ln x$ and $f(b) - f(a) = \\int_a^b \\ln t\\,dt$. Taking logarithms, the desired inequality becomes\n$$\\tfrac{1}{2}f(2n-1) < \\ln P_n < \\tfrac{1}{2}f(2n+1).$$\n\nLet $a_n = \\tfrac{1}{2}f(2n-1)$. Note $a_{n+1} = \\tfrac{1}{2}f(2n+1)$. The claim is $a_n < \\ln P_n < a_{n+1}$.\n\n**Base case** $n=1$: $\\ln P_1 = 0$. $a_1 = \\tfrac{1}{2}(1\\cdot 0 - 1) = -\\tfrac{1}{2} < 0$. $a_2 = \\tfrac{1}{2}(3\\ln 3 - 3) > 0$ since $\\ln 3 > 1$ (as $e < 3$). ✓\n\n**Induction step.** Suppose $a_n < \\ln P_n < a_{n+1}$. We have $\\ln P_{n+1} - \\ln P_n = \\ln(2n+1)$, and\n$$a_{n+1} - a_n = \\tfrac{1}{2}\\int_{2n-1}^{2n+1} \\ln t\\, dt, \\qquad a_{n+2} - a_{n+1} = \\tfrac{1}{2}\\int_{2n+1}^{2n+3} \\ln t\\, dt.$$\n\nSince $\\ln$ is increasing:\n- $\\int_{2n-1}^{2n+1} \\ln t\\,dt \\le 2\\ln(2n+1)$, so $a_{n+1} - a_n \\le \\ln(2n+1) = \\ln P_{n+1} - \\ln P_n$. Combined with $a_n < \\ln P_n$, this gives $a_{n+1} < \\ln P_{n+1}$. ✓\n- $\\int_{2n+1}^{2n+3} \\ln t\\,dt \\ge 2\\ln(2n+1)$, so $a_{n+2} - a_{n+1} \\ge \\ln(2n+1) = \\ln P_{n+1} - \\ln P_n$. Combined with $\\ln P_n < a_{n+1}$, this gives $\\ln P_{n+1} < a_{n+2}$. ✓\n\nBoth inequalities propagate, completing the induction. The claim holds as stated.\n\n**Sanity check on asymptotics.** By Stirling, $\\ln P_n \\approx n\\ln(2n) - n$, while $\\tfrac{1}{2}f(2n\\pm 1) \\approx n\\ln(2n) - n \\pm \\tfrac{1}{2}\\ln(2n)$, confirming both sides bracket $\\ln P_n$ tightly.\n\nANSWER: true (the inequality holds as stated for every positive integer $n$)\nCONFIDENCE: high"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":693,"cache_read_input_tokens":19541,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":693},"output_tokens":69,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e7e07c6a-8b86-4328-a9a8-16146800edeb","uuid":"dfc3c087-c877-4214-a134-0a917f420817","request_id":"req_011CbDQyXQsYNZX7EgtGVDbC"}
